{
  "stem": "1400.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as I said, we were working, and I was losing weight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The food was less and less, and the war was coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We heard the Allies' artillery in the distance and the bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a group which worked at night, many, many times they were stopped at the wall because the Allies' bombing came.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they shut off the lights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were just sitting around in the cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were working in two different-- two shifts, a day and night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And from December till mid-March or so, we were building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then they stopped this building of this factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think they ever finished it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my condition was such that, you know, it, it took twice as many men to do one man's job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were just leaning against those carts to push-- to be able to push it on the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And Landsberg and Kaufering is very close by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were ordered from the Landsberg camp to march into Kaufering camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they said this is a hospital camp, and we will be taken care of there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They called it hospital camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was a A-frame barracks on the ground, and a little walkway cut into the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And on two side, the people of were sleeping and laying down shoulder to shoulder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had a little wood stove, a barrel-- a little half-- a little barrel for heat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I contracted in this Kaufering camp-- I don't know the number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They have numbers for it-- contracted typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In this camp, Landsberg and Kaufering, the cleaning condition was almost zilch, almost nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
